'''''Race Car Simulator''''' is a 1984 video game published by [[Creative Solutions]].

==Gameplay==
''Race Car Simulator'' is a game in which an overhead view of the racetrack and a view from the driver's eye are both available, and the game includes the option to design race tracks.<ref name="CGW31"/>

==Reception==
